title: Glitchtale TEASER Episode #9 Hope | Work in Progress
description: Hey guys! Thought I'd upload this as a quick update since I'm assuming a lot of you missed it.This clip was an extra I added at the end of the last Glitchtale Showcase, and since it was kind of a big announcement I thought I could upload it as well to give you guys something to theorize about and learn that the episode is in fact being worked on and the title of it.Once I get more of the fight scenes done and have a decent amount to show I'll make a proper trailer. If everything goes well I should be done somewhere this year, probably towards the second half of the year. I want to take my sweet time with this and properly take breaks if I feel too overwhelmed by work.After this episode is done I'll work on Season 3, more known as the Glitchtale Prequel, which is a story also in the glitchtale universe but it takes place 1000 years in the past before the barrier was made and what were the events that led up to it.Most of the cast is gonna be new, but we'll see characters like Gaster and Asgore but in their younger years. I'll work on a few animatics to present the main cast and then we dive into Season 3 with fully animated episodes packed with action and what I would say is a pretty nice story.---------------------------------------------------------Support me on Patreon and made this series possible!(And get your cool name in the credits of each animation):https://www.patreon.com/camilacuevasYou may also support me by getting some Official Glitchtale Merch!: https://tinyurl.com/y8b6p4ho--------------------------------------------------My social media!Official Glitchtale Discord Server: https://discord.com/invite/fRn9NFuOfficial sub-reddit: https://tinyurl.com/y6c2a9buFacebook Page: https://tinyurl.com/y7hgcyqzMy DeviantArt: http://camilaanims.deviantart.com/My Tumblr: http://camilaart.tumblr.com/Twitter: @camilacuevaszuMy Instagram: @camilacuevas_artMy Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/camila2929Join the Glitchtale Amino Community:iOS: https://tinyurl.com/l9zr7twAndroid: https://tinyurl.com/m5d6vfj---------------------------------------------------------Thanks for reading ‚ô•
